01:46.840 --> 01:48.909
You didn't check to make
sure she was in there?

01:48.942 --> 01:50.444
Mmm...

01:50.478 --> 01:51.779
(yawns)
Hey.

01:54.315 --> 01:56.184
Aw, damn it,
Maw Maw!

01:56.217 --> 01:57.285
